			<subsection name="Technologies">
				<p>The used technologies are:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Java J2SE 1.5 or higher (incl. JMX)</li>
					<li>Spring 2.0.6</li>
					<li>ActiveMQ 5.3.0</li>
					<li>Simple Space 2.5</li>
					<li>Commons Logging 1.1</li>
					<li>XText 0.7.1</li>
					<li>EODM 1.5</li>
					<li>SWT 3.3.0-v3346</li>
					<li>OWL API 2.1.1</li>
					<li>Pellet 2.0.0-rc7</li>
					<li>JDOM 1.1</li>
					<li>Drools 4.0.7</li>
					<li>OpenID4Java 0.9.3</li>
					<li>BouncyCastle 140</li>
					<li>Hibernate 3.2.6</li>
					<li>Axis2 1.3</li>
					<li>Jetty 6.1.1</li>
					<li>JME 2.0.1</li>
				</ul>
			</subsection>
			<subsection name="Requirements">
				<p>The hosts should have</p>
				<ul>
					<li>1 GHz CPU</li>
					<li>512 MB RAM</li>
					<li>been registered in the DNS</li>
					<li>the possibility for multicast on port 6155 and 9999</li>
					<li>the possibility for communication on two additional ports</li>
					<li>installed JRE 1.5 or higher</li>
					<li>set the environment variable JAVA_HOME</li>
					<li>installed Maven 2.2.1 or higher</li>
				</ul>
			</subsection>
